OL,3,CBank payments could be delayed by
OL,4,Cthree days under new anti-fraud rules
OL,6,FBank payments could be delayed by up
OL,7,Fto three days under new rules that
OL,8,Fwould give banks more time to
OL,9,Finvestigate and break scammers'
OL,10,F"criminal spell".
OL,12,FThe government has proposed laws that
OL,13,Fwill extend the time that payments can
OL,14,Fbe stalled by up to 72 hours.
OL,16,FCurrently, banks have until the end of
OL,17,Fthe next business day to process or
OL,18,Freject a customer's payment.
