OL,3,CBank payments could be delayed by
OL,4,Cthree days under new anti-fraud rules
OL,6,FIf a bank finds evidence of fraudulent
OL,7,Fpayments, it must inform customers of
OL,8,Fthe delay and explain how to resolve
OL,9,Fit.
OL,11,FBanks will also be required to
OL,12,Fcompensate customers for any interest
OL,13,For late payment fees caused by the
OL,14,Fdelays.
OL,16,FExtending the time window will give
OL,17,Fbanks more time to investigate
OL,18,Fsuspicious transactions and block
OL,19,Fpotentially high-risk payments.
