OL,3,CBank payments could be delayed by
OL,4,Cthree days under new anti-fraud rules
OL,6,FTulip Siddiq, the economic secretary
OL,7,Fto the Treasury, said: "Hundreds of
OL,8,Fmillions of pounds are lost to
OL,9,Fscammers each year, targeting
OL,10,Fvulnerable communities and ruining the
OL,11,Flives of ordinary people.
OL,13,F"We need to protect these people
OL,14,Fbetter, which is why we are giving
OL,15,Fbanks more time to investigate
OL,16,Fsuspicious payments and break the
OL,17,Fcriminal spell that scammers weave."
