OL,3,CBank payments could be delayed by
OL,4,Cthree days under new anti-fraud rules
OL,6,FThe changes are designed to protect
OL,7,Fpeople from authorised push payment
OL,8,F(APP) fraud, where victims are tricked
OL,9,For pressured into sending money to
OL,10,Ffraudsters.
OL,12,FRocio Concha, the director of policy
OL,13,Fand advocacy at consumer group Which?,
OL,14,Fsaid the proposals mark a "positive
OL,15,Fstep in the fight against fraud".
