OL,6,F"While it should not affect the vast
OL,7,Fmajority of everyday payments, it's
OL,8,Fimportant that banks can delay a bank
OL,9,Ftransfer and take action if they think
OL,10,Fa customer is being targeted by a scam.
OL,12,F"These measures should be used in a
OL,13,Fcareful and targeted way."
OL,15,FPurchase scams, where people pay for
OL,16,Fgoods or services that never arrive or
OL,17,Fare fake, are on the rise, along with
OL,18,Fromance scams.
